      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_1_00010"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard Beer
                     Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb36300" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Kopenhagen</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">post rest.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb43570" type="place">Dänemark</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_1_00009"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb41072" type="place">Nordcap</rs></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Det Nordenfjeldske</hi></seg></seg><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Dampskibsselskab</hi></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb40290" type="place">Trondhjem</rs></hi></p><seg><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print">Soleil de Minuit. Midnightsun</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">SS. »Sverre Sigurdssön«</hi></seg></seg></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_1_00009"/>Eben nach 36 <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>td wunder<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chöner Fahrt auf der <rs type="place" ref="#pmb118890">Nord<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs> in <rs ref="#pmb42572" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Stavanger</hi></rs> gelandet, von da gehts um <time>6</time> weiter. Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibe Ihnen, Ihrer
               letzten Karte folgend, bereits nach <rs ref="#pmb36300" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Kopenhagen</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype">post rest</hi>; zweifle aber, d<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Sie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon dort<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind, warum ich
               zweifle, wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s ich nicht.</p><p>Ich freue mich auf Ihre Nachrichten.</p><closer>Herzlich der Ihre <signed>ArthSch</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
